<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p><em>Image Source: Hong Kong Tourism Board</em></p>'=>'<p><em>Image Source: Hong Kong Tourism Board</em></p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Open daily | East Coast Boardwalk, North Point</p><p>For a tranquil escape from the city’s hustle, discover one of the newest gems in town – the East Coast Boardwalk and the sprawling East Coast Park Precinct. This newly opened waterfront promenade offers breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour, seamlessly connecting North Point to Quarry Bay.</p><p>Take a leisurely stroll along the harbourfront, explore the lush greenery of the park precinct, and enjoy the stunning sunset while marveling at the iconic skyline views from both sides of the harbour. Whether you’re snapping photos, soaking in the sea breeze, or simply unwinding, this is the ideal spot to recharge after a day at the jewellery show.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p><em>Image Source: Harbourfront Commission, Government Information Centre</em></p>'=>'<p><strong>时间与地点</strong>：每日开放 | 北角东岸海滨长廊</p><p>若想远离城市喧嚣，寻找一处宁静之地，不妨探索城中最新亮点——东岸海滨长廊及广阔的东岸公园区域。这新开幕的海滨长廊以维多利亚港的壮丽景色作背景，无缝连接北角与鲗鱼涌。 </p><p>您可沿著海滨悠闲漫步，探索公园绿意盎然，欣赏两岸天际线的醉人日落。无论是拍照、感受海风，还是单纯放松，这里都是珠宝展后充电的理想地点。 </p><p> </p><p> </p><p><em>Image Source: Harbourfront Commission, Government Information Centre</em></p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Open daily | Temple Street, Jordan</p><p>Dive into Hong Kong’s buzzing street culture at the iconic Temple Street Night Market. This lively marketplace offers a sensory feast, from street-side food stalls, to fortune tellers and street performances.</p><p>Indulge in authentic Hong Kong delicacies, take in the vibrant atmosphere of this quintessential local experience. It’s a vibrant slice of Hong Kong’s heartbeat - fantastic way to immerse yourself in this city’s dynamic street culture. Don’t forget to pick up some one-of-a-kind treasures as souvenirs to take home!</p>'=>'<p><strong>时间与地点</strong>：每日开放 | 佐敦庙街</p><p>走进香港充满活力的街头文化，体验标志性的庙街夜市。从街头美食摊档到算命师及街头表演，应有尽有。 </p><p>您可品尝正宗香港美食，沉浸于热闹气氛，这是香港脉动的生动缩影。别忘了挑选一些独一无二的纪念品，带回家留念喔！  </p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Until April 13, 2025 | AIRSIDE, Kai Tak</p><p><strong>Calling all movie buffs!</strong> This immersive exhibition takes you back in time with a meticulously restored film set from the classic “Twilight of the Warriors: Walled In”.</p><p>Walk through authenic locations from the movie scenes, like a barber shop, tea stall, and bone-setting clinic, all painstakingly designed to capture the gritty charm of old Hong Kong. You’ll also get a behind-the-scences look at the craftsmanship and artistry that went into the movie’s production, as well as insights into Hong Kong’s rich film history and the legendary Kowloon Walled City. It’s a nostalgic journey into Hong Kong’s cinematic soul – a great way to experience the spirit of the city.</p>'=>'<p><strong>时间与地点</strong>：即日起至2025年4月13日 | 启德AIRSIDE</p><p><strong>影迷注意！</strong> 影迷注意！此沉浸式展览将带您穿越时空，回到经典电影《九龙城寨之围城》中精心复原的拍摄场景。</p><p>您可漫步于电影中真实再现的场景，如理发店、茶档及跌打医馆，感受旧香港的粗犷魅力。此外，您更有机会一窥电影制作的幕后工艺与艺术，深入了解香港丰富的电影历史以及传奇九龙城寨的背景故事。这是一场探索香港电影灵魂的怀旧之旅，让您亲身感受这座城市的独特文化气息。  </p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Until March 2, 2025 | Lee Tung Avenue, Wan Chai</p><p>Step into a magical wonderland at <a href="https://www.leetungavenue.com.hk/en/index/">Lee Tung Avenue</a>, where over 800 traditional Chinese lanterns cast a warm glow across this tree-lined pedestrian avenue in celebration of the Year of the Snake. Glowing in hues of gold and red - symbolizing happiness and prosperity – the lanterns create a serene and enchanting vibe, perfect for an evening stroll.</p><p>Don’t miss the peach blossom garden with its charming heart-shaped arch – an ideal spot for Instagrammable photos! This is the ultimate place to soak in the festive ambiance after a busy day at the jewellery show. Plus, who doesn’t love a bit of good fortune and blessings under the glow of lanterns?</p>'=>'<p><strong>时间与地点</strong>：即日起至2025年3月2日 | 湾仔利东街</p><p>走进<a href="https://www.leetungavenue.com.hk/tc/index/">利东街</a>，仿佛置身奇幻仙境。这条绿树成荫的步行街悬挂超过800盏传统中式灯笼，为庆祝蛇年而点亮温暖光芒。 </p><p>别错过桃花园中迷人的心形拱门，那是拍摄网红照片的绝佳地点！在珠宝展忙碌一天后，这里是感受节日气氛的最佳场所。谁能抗拒在灯笼辉映下祈求好运与祝福的美好时刻呢？  </p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Until March 6, 2025 | Central Market, Central</p><p><strong>Attention panda lovers!</strong> This whimsical festival is a must-see. With over 800 panda sculptures featuring festive Lunar New Year designs scattered across Central Market. It’s a creative and adorable celebration of Hong Kong’s panda craze.</p><p>But that’s not all! Make time to visit <a href="https://www.oceanpark.com.hk/">Ocean Park</a>, where you can meet the beloved panda twins and the two newly added family members. It’s a moment of pure joy and relaxation that’s perfect for escaping the hustle and bustle of the jewellery show.</p>'=>'<p><strong>时间与地点</strong>：即日起至2025年3月6日 | 中环街市</p><p><strong>熊猫爱好者注意！</strong> 这个充满趣味的活动不容错过。中环街市遍布超过800个以农历新年为主题的熊猫雕塑，展现香港对熊猫的热爱。  </p><p>此外，不妨抽空前往<a href="https://www.oceanpark.com.hk/">海洋公园</a>，探访深受喜爱的熊猫双胞胎及其两个新加入的家庭成员。这是远离珠宝展喧嚣、享受纯粹快乐与放松的完美选择。  </p>','<p>As you gear up for the <strong>Hong Kong International Jewellery Show</strong> (March 4-8, 2025), why not add an extra sparkle to your itinerary? Beyond the brilliance of gems and countless business opportunities, Hong Kong is a city bursting with cultural, treasures, scenic spots, and unique experiences that will make your visit truly unforgettable.</p><p>We’ve handpicked<strong> five incredible must-visit places and events</strong> happening during your stay. Whether you’re seeking inspiration, or just some fun, there’s something on this list for everyone – perfect for unwinding after a productive day at the jewellery show.</p><p><strong>Ready to explore? Let’s dive in!</strong></p>'=>'<p>您准备好参加2025年3月4日至8日举行的<strong>香港国际珠宝展</strong>了吗？除了展会上琳琅满目的珠宝与无数商机，香港这座城市还充满文化宝藏、风景名胜和独特体验，定能为您的旅程增添难忘回忆。 </p><p>我们为您精心挑选了<strong>5个不容错过的景点和活动</strong>，让您在繁忙的展会以外，尽情感受香港魅力。无论您想寻找灵感还是轻松一下，这份清单都能满足您的需求，助您在珠宝展结束后好好放松。 </p><p><strong>您准备好了吗？ </strong></p>','<p>These five unforgettable experiences are the perfect complement to your time during the <a href="https://www.hktdc.com/event/hkjewellery/en"><strong>Hong Kong International Jewellery Show 2025</strong></a>. From the glowing lanterns to the cinematic nostalgia and iconic street markets, each spot offers a unique taste of Hong Kong’s culture and creativity.</p><p>So, pack your bags, polish your business cards, and prepare for a trip filled with dazzling gems – both at the jewellery show and across the city. Which experience will you choose first? Let us know in the comments or tag us in your Hong Kong travel highlights!</p><p>Don’t forget to visit us to explore our fabulous new collections and experience our exceptional bespoke services. It is also a perfect opportunity to share your discoveries and insights from your visits.</p>'=>'<p>以上5个难忘体验，与<a href="https://www.hktdc.com/event/hkjewellery/en"><strong>香港国际珠宝展</strong></a>相得益彰。从灯笼辉映的节日气氛到电影怀旧之旅，再到标志性的街头夜市，每个地点都展现了香港独特的文化与创意。<br><br> </p><p>收拾好行李，准备好名片，为这场充满璀璨珠宝与城市魅力的旅程做好准备吧！  </p><p>您会先选择哪个体验？欢迎在评论中告诉我们，或在您的香港之旅中标记我们，分享您的精彩时刻！ </p>','<p>📅</p><p>    MARCH 4 (TUE)           1030-1830</p><p>MARCH 5-7 (WED-FRI)     1000-1830</p><p class="last-child">     MARCH 8 (SAT)           1000-1730</p>'=>'<p>📅</p><p> 3月4日（二）10:30am – 6:30pm</p><p>3月5日～7日（三～五）10am – 6:30pm</p><p class="last-child"> 3月8日（六）10am – 5:30pm</p>','<p>📍</p><p><strong>WORLD OF GLAMOUR HALL 1C #C02</strong></p><p>HONG KONG CONVENTION AND EXHIBITION CENTRE</p><p>1 EXPO DRIVE</p><p class="last-child">WAN CHAI, HONG KONG</p>'=>'<p>📍</p><p><strong>瑰丽珠宝馆 1C厅 #C02</strong></p><p>香港会议展览中心</p><p>湾仔博览道一号</p><p class="last-child">香港</p>','Hong Kong International Jewellery Show 2025'=>'香港国际珠宝展','Image Source: Instagram @pandago_fest'=>'Image Source: Instagram @pandago_fest','Image Source: Lee Tung Avenue'=>'Image Source: Lee Tung Avenue','Lee Tung Avenue: “Lanterns-Lit Year of the Snake”'=>'利东街：元宵节灯笼展','Pa